"Test clsolve con unidades completas

"1. K con unidades homogeneas
K = [1000 kN/m; -500 kN/m|-500 kN/m; 1500 kN/m]
F = [10 kN; -5 kN]

"1.1 Solve directo
u = lsolve(K; F)
u

"1.2 Solve con & mm
u_mm = lsolve(K; F) & [mm; mm]
u_mm

"2. K construida con B^T*D*B (con unidades)
E = 200000 MPa
t = 0.2 m
D = E*t/(1 - 0.04)*[1; 0.2|0.2; 1]
B = [1; 0; -1|0; 1; 0]/(1 m)
K_2 = transp(B)*D*B*(0.5 m)^2
K_2
F_2 = [10 kN; -5 kN; 3 kN]
u_2 = lsolve(K_2; F_2) & [mm; mm; mm]
u_2
